### Variáveis Globais
@baseUrl = GET http://localhost:3001
@name = teste2
@email = teste2@teste.com
@password = 123456

### 1. Criar um novo usuário (Sign Up)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/mercados/registerMarket
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": " {{name}}",
    "email" : "{{email}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}


### 3. Listar Usuários (Rota Protegida)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/mercados/showmarkets

